      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INCREDIBLE MOUSE (1) hit the ground running and set it up early clocking 17.14 with a 4.5 lengths win at this track over 300m. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Well placed and can measure up. BLUEY BRANN (2) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 2 lengths (17.21) behind Redhot Money at this track. Overdue and is among the main hopes. CAPPADORA (5) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing sixth (17.62) at this track latest. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Great chance to atone. RED NED GUNDI (3) was a surprise last-start placegetter who is in the mix again.",
